column4: Intel  Altera end takeover talks due to price disagreement: source
column5: Discussions on a takeover by Intel Corp of smaller chip maker Altera Corp have ended as the companies were unable to agree on price  a person familiar with the matter said  but Altera shares rose  suggesting it is still a potential target.
